ation regarding the pay practices for certain executives       privacy policy terms of use about us contact us  salarycom all rights reserved us salaries canadian salaries purchase a salary report salaries by category salaries by income salaries by industry popular salaries negotiation tips benefits calculator search job openings job openings by state job openings by category education by career education by level education by major cost of living calculator robert d isom jr executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    am et airlines company overview of american airlines group inc snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile robert d isom jrpresident american airlines group incagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriesas of fiscal year  background mr robert d isom jr has been president of american airlines group inc since august   and american airlines inc since september   mr isom oversees american’s operations planning marketing sales alliances and pricing he served as the chief operating officer of american airlines group inc from december  to august   mr isom served as the chief operating officer of american airlines inc since december  until september   and  served as executive vice president until september   he served as an executive vice president of american airlines group inc from december  to august   he served as the chief operating officer and executive vice president of us airways llc formerly america west airlines inc since june   he served as chief operating officer and executive vice president of us airways group inc since december   mr isom served as chief operating officer and executive vice president of us airways inc since september   and served as its chief executive officer from december  to august   he was responsible for all aspects of airline operations including customer service flight operations maintenance regional carrier man